Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hate" and "love" are both depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But reasoning and suspense are between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police detectives and and the detective boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love and mystery are on the verge of exploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On TV, didn't they say Hide would be on the last car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with this being soccer, it's strange to have a victory parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the Tokyo Spirits have always been one of the strongest teams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first time they've won the J1.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention how dramatic the final game was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide scored a tying goal from zero in the second half to send it to overtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Naoki scored the winning goal right when overtime started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was so awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't really see the parade through this crowd, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too bad, because I wanted to film them with my video camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd have been better off watching on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I set a video tape to record it before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can all watch it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe we can get a better view over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can stand on the trash can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see some of their heads, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of their faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, if only it were a bit bigger I could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a platform bigger than that trash bin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could one be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:51.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,PARADE OF MALICE AND SAINT\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see them out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's Naoki right behind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're waving this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, let me see, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just give me one more minute, it's just getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be standing up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, I'll get them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the problem, old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why're you calling me "old lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't obey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Satou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called in for work so you could secretly watch the parade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you're disguised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On a date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was trying on wigs in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's risky to date on duty even if you are disguised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two aren't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't you get fired for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it OK for police officers to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This makes me worry about the future of Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, it isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Shiratori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you disguised as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone faxed a strange message to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I am anti-Spirits. Something of interest will occur at the victory parade today."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fax resembles a message we received for a case a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, our division is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:06:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we had to disguise just in case the criminal from that past case remembers our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, it's probably just a prank pulled by someone who isn't satisfied with the team's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The date in question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually next week, isn't it?.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you two pushed the date ahead because you couldn't wait for the next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought too far ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you all get that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, everyone knows now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to the new Tropica Marine Land, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(wouldn't underestimate police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,e asked for the day off on one of your scheduled off days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a simple conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told everyone when he was taken into the interrogation room and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Interrogated"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems a lot of others have asked for that day off as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, all of the wirelesses and binoculars are reserved for that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're doing a stake out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we go to Tropical Marine land as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} there as thanks for saving me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, that's really it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gotta believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you given up on the marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't raise the white flag just because our match-up didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they are still using "kun" and "san"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm the overseeing director of the stake out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Date! Date!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't the man of rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he comes now, they will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with a disguise, we'll recognize you instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you guys to be here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of you officers were surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of my disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not bad, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to have a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you dressed like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now get that disguise off and get in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just then, you looked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you were promoted to our division...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a guy with us in Division 1 for only a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems Hide's car is finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's jump in there and film them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I've been recording for so long that my tape is almost spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you bring extra tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then hurry up so we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is it safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said someone faxed a threat about something happening at this parade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So far, it seems like it really was just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what are you doing here, Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm invo ved in a parking violation enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought a number of those here for the parade would leave their cars on the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1'1 cite you as well if you don't move yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aren't you a Big Osaka fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you came to this parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to place a curse on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that they won't win next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and film the car before they're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keys, keys, keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This just isn't my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone stole your video camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the crowd just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Halt the parade and evacuate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a car's been blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that car...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the car Detective Takagi was driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could Detective Takagi have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I saw someone approach the car from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Shiratori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The explosion occurred when he approached the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually, I wouldn't imagine anyone could survive such a blast...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said "usually."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I barely escaped that alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's not talk like that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed something under the car by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The paper bag wasn't there when I parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to go ask Inspector Shiratori if he thought it was a bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's when it exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you knew a bomb was inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We mentioned that the fax we received today is similar to one from a past case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, any officer who was briefed on that case would find it strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't know that you're not injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay back, Satou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Miwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get him out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are those burns on your hand!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we need to get that treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll leave this to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the one Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying to rescue this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could have been Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The type of bomb was a plastic explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The explosion was triggered by a wireless detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By a cell phone or a similar device.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomber may have been watching you approach the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you got to it, he triggered the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the bomb was triggered by a wireless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the case from three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely they are after the ves of police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone on this case needs to remember to work cautiously, yet swiftly, in order to get the bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I may have recorded the criminal on video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was recording around where the explosion happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone in the crowd ended up stealing the video camera during the parade, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the tape is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He changed tapes right before the camera was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The video camera is fine as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thief discarded it at a station nearby after removing the blank tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the tape, not the camera, was what he was after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:18:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one who would bother is a big Spirits fan that wanted to film the parade all himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or the bomber who was caught on tape against his will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ot seeing anything even on this big screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,02:32 F\NThe only thing Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was filming were his feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put the camera down without powering it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can hear you all talking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no incriminating shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to have a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you only tape this part?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seems to be crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there someone by the car behind Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too far away to make an identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, the camera's pointed down at the ground again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the bomber wasn't caught on tape placing the bomb like we hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But maybe there's something unusual in the crowd from when I was first filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's rewind and watch it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Megure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been another explosion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time we're dealing with a telephone booth that's near a playground in Haido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one was injured by the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep watching out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't the road from the intersectio lead to that playground in Haido?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's the path of the Spirits parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means their aim wasn't to kill police...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was to interrupt the victory parade of the Tokyo Spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are your hands all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't they burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know what the bomber is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there may well be more bombs out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every officer in the area needs to get on the parade route and evacuate the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, stop at nothing to find the rest of the bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want a bomb squad ready in the event of an emergency, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, stay here and review the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what is the criminal after?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomber from thre years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fax the police received...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bombing of the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, there's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did they draw the police to that telephone booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was their aim really to disrupt the Spirits' parade?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko's video tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capture the image of the criminal on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it they're after?
